<% layout('/layouts/boilerplate.ejs') -%>

<div class="row mt-3">
    <section class="col-10 privacy-terms container">
        <h1 class="mb-4">🔐 Privacy & Terms of Use</h1>

        <p>
            At <strong>GlobeHaven</strong>, your privacy matters to us. We are committed
            to protecting your personal information and being transparent about how we
            use it. This page explains what data we collect, why we collect it, and how
            we keep it safe.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h3>📌 Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We may collect limited information when you:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Create an account or log in</li>
            <li>Add or explore travel listings</li>
            <li>Contact us or submit forms</li>
        </ul>

        <p>This may include:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Name and email address</li>
            <li>Location details you voluntarily provide</li>
            <li>Basic usage data to improve site performance</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>We do not collect sensitive personal information unnecessarily.</strong></p>

        <hr />

        <h3>🧭 How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Provide and improve our travel services</li>
            <li>Display relevant locations and listings</li>
            <li>Ensure platform security and prevent misuse</li>
            <li>Communicate important updates when required</li>
        </ul>

        <p><strong>We never sell or trade your personal data.</strong></p>

        <hr />

        <h3>🔒 Data Security</h3>
        <p>
            We use reasonable security practices to protect your data from unauthorized
            access, loss, or misuse. While no system is completely secure, we
            continuously work to safeguard your information.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h3>🌍 Third-Party Services</h3>
        <p>
            GlobeHaven may use trusted third-party services (such as maps or image
            hosting) strictly to enhance functionality. These services follow their own
            privacy policies, and we recommend reviewing them.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h3>🍪 Cookies</h3>
        <p>We may use cookies to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Maintain login sessions</li>
            <li>Improve user experience</li>
            <li>Analyze basic site usage</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>

        <hr />

        <h3>👤 Your Control</h3>
        <p>You always have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access or update your account information</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Choose not to share optional details</li>
        </ul>

        <hr />

        <h3>📜 Terms of Use</h3>
        <p>By using GlobeHaven, you agree to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Use the platform responsibly</li>
            <li>Share accurate and respectful content</li>
            <li>Avoid misuse, spamming, or harmful activity</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            We reserve the right to update content or suspend accounts that violate these
            terms.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h3>🔄 Updates to This Policy</h3>
        <p>
            We may update this Privacy & Terms page occasionally. Any changes will be
            reflected here to keep you informed.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h3>💬 Contact Us</h3>
        <p>
            If you have any questions about privacy or data usage, feel free to reach
            out through our contact page.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4">
            ✨ <em>GlobeHaven is built for explorers — not for exploiting data. Your trust
            is important to us.</em>
        </p>
    </section>
</div>